XCSoar Python API for SkyLines
==============================

Compile with

 make output/UNIX/bin/libXCSoarTools.so WERROR=n

and copy the library to your desired location, renaming it
to XCSoarTools.so.


Short API description
---------------------


* class XCSoarTools()

Initializes the API


* XCSoarTools.LoadIGC(filename)

Loads a IGC file into memory


* XCSoarTools.Path()

Returns a list of fixes


* XCSoarTools.Times()

Returns a list of takeoff/release/landing times found in the flight


* XCSoarTools.Analyse(begin, end, full=512, triangle=1024, sprint=96)

Analyse a flight from begin to end (both DateTime objects), optional
specifying the number of trace points for the optimiser.
